50|$|<b>Safety</b> <b>Light</b> {{curtains}} are opto-electronic {{devices that}} are used to safeguard personnel in the vicinity of moving machinery with the potential to cause harm such as presses, winders and palletisers. <b>Safety</b> <b>Light</b> curtains can be used as an alternative to mechanical barriers and other forms of traditional machine guarding. By reducing the need for physical guards and barriers, <b>safety</b> <b>light</b> curtains can increase the maintainability of the equipment they are guarding. The operability and efficiency of machinery can also be improved by the use of <b>safety</b> <b>light</b> curtains by, for example, allowing easier access for semi-automatic procedures.|$|E
