50|$|<b>Safety</b> <b>Light</b> {{curtains}} are supplied as a {{pair with}} a transmitter and receiver. The transmitter projects an array of parallel infrared light beams to the receiver which consists {{of a number of}} photoelectric cells. When an object breaks {{one or more of the}} beams a stop signal is sent to the guarded equipment.|$|E
