50|$|In {{the field}} of {{physical}} security, security lighting is lighting that intended to deter or detect intrusions or other criminal activity {{on a piece of}} real property. It {{can also be used to}} increase a feeling of <b>safety.</b> <b>Lighting</b> is integral to crime prevention through environmental design.|$|R
